Bubble graph and pie chart:

plt.scatter(x,y, s=np.random.rand(5)*1000, c=np.random.rand(5))
rest is same as scatter plot we just mention size and color in bubble graph

pie chart=> data=[3,7,6,5,8]
plt.pie(data)
plt.show

ex=(0,0.1,0,0,0) => explode->separates the piece
lb=['a','b','c','d','e'] =>labels

plt.pie(data, labels=lb, explode=ex, shadow=true)
